249
00:14:07,500 --> 00:14:08,350
Puan.

250
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:16,120
Tuan puteri.

251
00:14:19,260 --> 00:14:20,580
Puan Cui, sila bangun.

252
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:21,930
Baik.

253
00:14:23,370 --> 00:14:24,140
Tuan puteri.

254
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:25,650
Patik masih ada urusan penting,

255
00:14:25,650 --> 00:14:27,330
minta diri dulu.

256
00:14:32,650 --> 00:14:35,580
Memandangkan dia anggap saya sebagai
Puteri Fu Wei,

257
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,800
saya akan gunakan status ini

258
00:14:38,100 --> 00:14:39,830
untuk memberinya pengajaran.

259
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:49,820
Pintu utama terbuka luas,

260
00:14:50,110 --> 00:14:52,170
tapi pintu sisi pula tertutup rapat.

261
00:14:53,710 --> 00:14:55,140
Nampaknya keluarga Wang ini

262
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:58,070
memang menyimpan rahsia yang
tak boleh didedahkan.

263
00:14:59,450 --> 00:15:01,450
Memandangkan pintu ditutup rapat,

264
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:03,560
bagaimana kita mahu buat siasatan?

265
00:15:03,970 --> 00:15:06,010
Semua ahli keluarga Wang masuk
melalui pintu sisi.

266
00:15:06,010 --> 00:15:06,780
Lagipun,

267
00:15:07,520 --> 00:15:10,120
kedudukan ini lebih dekat
dengan dewan utama.

268
00:15:10,410 --> 00:15:11,490
Mungkin kita boleh

269
00:15:11,910 --> 00:15:14,110
mendengar sedikit maklumat dari sini.

270
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:15,850
Nampaknya tuan puteri

271
00:15:15,850 --> 00:15:17,730
bukan saja seiras Cik Ruoxi,

272
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:19,660
malah tahu selok-belok

273
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:21,510
keluarga sebelah ibunya.

274
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:34,240
Hei.

275
00:15:34,290 --> 00:15:35,170
Kamu berdua!

276
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:39,460
Apa yang kamu berdua buat secara
sembunyi-sembunyi di depan kediaman kami?

277
00:15:40,020 --> 00:15:41,550
Nampaknya cara tuan puteri

278
00:15:42,850 --> 00:15:43,650
tak berkesan.

279
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:45,590
Apakah

280
00:15:45,810 --> 00:15:47,540
yang patut kita buat sekarang?

281
00:15:56,310 --> 00:15:57,190
Peluk beta.

282
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:13,420
Saya bercakap dengan kamulah!

283
00:16:13,420 --> 00:16:15,080
Apakah yang kamu buat di sini?

284
00:16:28,670 --> 00:16:31,730
Rupanya sedang bercengkerama
dengan kekasih di sini.

285
00:16:32,490 --> 00:16:35,050
Tadi saya fikir ada pencuri.

286
00:16:35,940 --> 00:16:36,940
Cepat pergi!

287
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:40,770
Cepatlah pergi!

288
00:17:15,530 --> 00:17:16,440
Tuan puteri.

289
00:17:21,020 --> 00:17:22,750
Mempergunakan orang lalu membuangnya

290
00:17:22,750 --> 00:17:24,280
bukanlah amalan yang baik.

291
00:17:44,250 --> 00:17:45,200
Sekarang

292
00:17:45,780 --> 00:17:46,610
kita dah seri.

293
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:21,640
Teruskan.

294
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,040
Puan.

295
00:18:23,210 --> 00:18:24,200
Puteri dah tiba.

296
00:18:34,860 --> 00:18:36,990
Tuan puteri tiba-tiba mencemar duli,

297
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:38,440
ada apa hal?

298
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:39,420
Melutut!

299
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:41,610
Adakah beta suruh kamu bangun?

300
00:18:44,900 --> 00:18:47,630
Keranda ibu saudara beta
dah tiba di negara Qing.

301
00:18:47,760 --> 00:18:49,520
Namun, setelah beta fikirkan,

302
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:52,390
Tuan Zhou dan ibu saudara beta
pernah menjadi suami dan gundik,

303
00:18:52,390 --> 00:18:53,850
papan roh ibu saudara beta

304
00:18:53,890 --> 00:18:55,720
wajar diletakkan di balai leluhur
keluarga Zhou.

305
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:56,640
Puan Cui.

306
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:57,920
Apakah pendapat puan?

307
00:19:00,220 --> 00:19:01,100
Ini...

308
00:19:02,970 --> 00:19:04,700
Ini bertentangan dengan adat,

309
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,680
patik tak boleh buat keputusan.

310
00:19:07,230 --> 00:19:08,310
Patik perlu

311
00:19:08,770 --> 00:19:09,830
bertanya kepada tuan dulu.

312
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:12,950
Bagaimana jika beta mahu awak
yang buat keputusan ini?

313
00:19:13,510 --> 00:19:14,310
Patik...

314
00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:20,650
Lebih baik tunggu tuan pulang
untuk membuat keputusan.

315
00:19:20,880 --> 00:19:21,720
Puan Cui.

316
00:19:22,050 --> 00:19:23,070
Beta

317
00:19:23,290 --> 00:19:25,350
mahu papan roh ibu saudara beta

318
00:19:25,420 --> 00:19:28,080
masuk ke balai leluhur
keluarga Zhou sekarang!

319
00:19:29,260 --> 00:19:30,260
Wang Rongyi

320
00:19:30,290 --> 00:19:31,960
hanyalah gundik keluarga Zhou.

321
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:33,850
Patik tak berani bertindak melulu...

322
00:19:33,850 --> 00:19:34,800
- Awak!
- Puan.

323
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:35,840
Awak apa?

324
00:19:36,210 --> 00:19:37,690
Berani awak mengingkari titah beta?

